name: love in the times of corona II
description: “i remember we were young, but not as young as all the other girls. we didn't know anything about sex - i guess we knew a couple things, all but the one that really mattered. one of us had just done it for the first time. she was trying to explain to us what it felt like, but she couldn't find the words, she said ‘i wanted him inside a place that doesn't exist’. i'd spend a long time thinking that's what it was supposed to feel like and, at times, it really did. for years i'd still chase that feeling. i guess i still do."
